            {
                "text": "And if the priest look, and, behold, the plague be somewhat dark after the washing of it; then he shall rend it out of the garment, or out of the skin, or out of the warp, or out of the woof:",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 48,
