            {
                "text": "And if it appear still in the garment, either in the warp, or in the woof, or in any thing of skin; it is a spreading plague: thou shalt burn that wherein the plague is with fire.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 103,
